  "prompt": "Which Indian startups are hiring freshers in Kolkata?",
  "response": "Kolkata's startup ecosystem has been steadily growing, offering numerous opportunities for freshers across various sectors such as technology, fintech, healthtech, e-commerce, and more. While specific hiring needs can change rapidly, here are some Kolkata-based startups that are known to hire freshers or have roles suitable for entry-level candidates. Additionally, I'll provide tips on how to find current openings.\n\n### Prominent Kolkata Startups Hiring Freshers\n\n1. **Entropik Tech**\n   - **Sector:** Artificial Intelligence & Emotion Recognition\n   - **About:** Specializes in AI-driven emotion analytics to improve user experiences.\n   - **Website:** [entropiktech.com](https://www.entropiktech.com/)\n\n2. **Arriv**\n   - **Sector:** Mobility & Transportation\n   - **About:** Focuses on last-mile delivery solutions and on-demand transportation services.\n   - **Website:** [arriv.co](https://www.arriv.co/)\n\n3. **Kiara Arpeggio**\n   - **Sector:** EdTech\n   - **About:** Provides personalized learning solutions and educational content.\n   - **Website:** [kiaraarpeggio.com](https://www.kiaraarpeggio.com/)\n\n4. **GreenJams**\n   - **Sector:** Consumer Electronics & Sustainable Tech\n   - **About:** Develops eco-friendly electronic gadgets and solutions.\n   - **Website:** [greenjams.com](https://www.greenjams.com/)\n\n5. **Sastra Robotics**\n   - **Sector:** Robotics & Automation\n   - **About:** Designs and manufactures industrial robotic systems.\n   - **Website:** [sastrarobotics.com](https://www.sastrarobotics.com/)\n\n6. **1Point3Acres**\n   - **Sector:** Education & Community Platform\n   - **About:** A platform for students aspiring to study abroad, offering resources and community support.\n   - **Website:** [1point3acres.com](https://www.1point3acres.com/)\n\n### How to Find Current Job Openings\n\n1. **Job Portals:**\n   - **LinkedIn:** Regularly updated with job postings from startups. Follow Kolkata-based companies and engage with their posts.\n   - **Naukri.com:** A popular job portal in India where many startups post their vacancies.\n   - **Indeed:** Aggregates job listings from various sources, including startups.\n   - **AngelList:** Specifically caters to startup jobs; filter by location to find Kolkata-based opportunities.\n\n2. **Company Websites:**\n   - Visit the careers section of the startups you're interested in to find the most accurate and updated job listings.\n\n3. **Networking Events and Meetups:**\n   - Attend local startup events, webinars, and networking meetups in Kolkata to connect directly with founders and hiring managers.\n   - Platforms like **Meetup.com** and **Eventbrite** often list relevant events.\n\n4. **Incubators and Accelerators:**\n   - Engage with incubators like **NASSCOM 10,000 Startups** or local accelerators that support Kolkata-based startups. They often have job boards or can connect you with hiring startups.\n\n5. **Social Media:**\n   - Follow startups on platforms like LinkedIn, Twitter, and Facebook where they frequently post job openings and company updates.\n\n### Tips for Freshers Applying to Startups\n\n- **Tailor Your Resume:** Highlight relevant projects, internships, and skills that align with the startup's focus.\n- **Show Enthusiasm:** Startups value passion and a willingness to learn. Demonstrate your excitement for the role and the company's mission.\n- **Be Adaptable:** Emphasize your ability to wear multiple hats and adapt to changing environments, which is common in startup settings.\n- **Prepare for Interviews:** Startups may conduct multiple interview rounds, including technical assessments and cultural fit interviews. Be ready to showcase both your technical skills and your alignment with the company's values.\n\n### Additional Kolkata-Based Startups to Explore\n\n- **Meesho:** A social commerce platform that enables small businesses and individuals to sell products via social channels.\n- **Shopkirana:** Focuses on empowering kirana stores through technology by providing inventory and ordering solutions.\n- **Sagarmatha Advisors:** Financial services startup offering investment and advisory services.\n\n*Please note that the hiring status of startups can change rapidly based on funding, growth stages, and market conditions. It's advisable to regularly check the aforementioned platforms and the startups' official channels for the latest information.*\n\n---\n\n**Good Luck with Your Job Search!** If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.",
